'''evangelical''' ''adjective'' of (or pertaining to) good news, ''esp.'' the Christian [[gospel]] of Jesus; [[protestant]], (''esp.'' mainland Europe); of, pertaining to, or resembling [[evangelicalism]], a protestant Christian movement emphasising personal faith and the authority of the [[Bible]]; of, pertaining to or resembling [[evangelism]] or [[proselytism]], ''esp'' when fervent or zealous.

'''evangelical''' ''noun'' adherent of [[evangelicalism]], a [[protestant]] [[Christian]] movement emphasising personal faith and the authority of the [[Bible]].

